---
title: "FASTag — Vehicle Passage Sequence (Happy Path)"
---
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant V as Vehicle
    participant RU as RFID Reader<br/>(150m upstream)
    participant EP as Edge Processor
    participant K as Kafka
    participant PA as Pre-Auth Service
    participant NPCI as NPCI Gateway
    participant RC as Redis Cache<br/>(Edge)
    participant LC as Lane Controller
    participant AS as Audit Service

    Note over V,AS: T = 0s — Vehicle enters upstream detection zone (150m from gate)

    V->>RU: RFID tag in range
    RU->>EP: Tag ID + signal strength (TCP/IP)
    EP->>RC: Check: recent read for this tag+lane? (idempotency)
    RC-->>EP: No recent read
    EP->>K: Publish TagRead event {tag_id, lane_id, plaza_id, timestamp}

    Note over EP,NPCI: T = 1s — Pre-authorization begins in cloud

    K->>PA: Consume TagRead event
    PA->>RC: Check balance cache (Redis cloud cluster)
    RC-->>PA: Cache miss (or stale)
    PA->>NPCI: POST /preauth {tag_id, amount, plaza_id, idempotency_key}

    Note over PA,NPCI: T = 1–4s — NPCI processes pre-authorization

    NPCI-->>PA: 200 OK {pre_auth_token, hold_amount, expires_at}
    PA->>RC: SET pre_auth_token (TTL: 120s, key: tag_id+lane_id)
    PA->>K: Publish PreAuthorizationApproved event

    Note over V,LC: T = 12–14s — Vehicle arrives at barrier

    V->>LC: Loop sensor triggered (vehicle at gate)
    LC->>RC: GET pre_auth_token for tag_id+lane_id
    RC-->>LC: Token found (age: ~11s, within TTL)
    LC->>LC: Validate token (not expired, plaza+lane match)

    Note over LC,V: T = 14s — Barrier opens (< 2s after vehicle arrival)

    LC->>V: Barrier arm raised ✓
    LC->>K: Publish BarrierOpened event {pre_auth_token, processing_time_ms}

    Note over K,AS: T = 14–20s — Async settlement and audit (not in critical path)

    K->>AS: Consume BarrierOpened event
    AS->>AS: Write audit record (append-only)

    Note over AS: Total vehicle wait at barrier: < 2 seconds
    Note over AS: End-to-end processing time: ~14 seconds (P50)
